{"tid":102131,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"A 酸問題, 求用家召喚☝","createTime":"2017-01-31T11:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T13:03:58.000Z","uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"51024fe46856e6efb4a59ba0543b7f3ddf2ca775","tid":102131,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T11:45:52.000Z","msg":"連登有冇食A 酸既朋友? 有野想指教一下<br />\n我食左四個月20mg 醫生叫我自己決定停唔停藥<br />\n但其實有一邊面 康復進度唔理想<br />\n但佢成日話算好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同劑量有冇關係? 佢有講再食就要40mg 一日"},{"pid":"f907bac33355b74623633925627b7e6b6a06fc45","tid":102131,"uid":52608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:10:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登有冇食A 酸既朋友? 有野想指教一下<br />\n我食左四個月20mg 醫生叫我自己決定停唔停藥<br />\n但其實有一邊面 康復進度唔理想<br />\n但佢成日話算好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同劑量有冇關係? 佢有講再食就要40mg 一日</blockquote><br />\n我都食左快半年，私家醫生，佢話正常黎講一個療程係6-9個月，我係完全一粒都唔生得番d印佢先話可以停，如果壓抑得唔夠耐同穩定會容易復發。"},{"pid":"11953c521975eac8cf61a58b4a4067cf5a7f8dad","tid":102131,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:13:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登有冇食A 酸既朋友? 有野想指教一下<br />\n我食左四個月20mg 醫生叫我自己決定停唔停藥<br />\n但其實有一邊面 康復進度唔理想<br />\n但佢成日話算好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同劑量有冇關係? 佢有講再食就要40mg 一日</blockquote><br />\n我都食左快半年，私家醫生，佢話正常黎講一個療程係6-9個月，我係完全一粒都唔生得番d印佢先話可以停，如果壓抑得唔夠耐同穩定會容易復發。</blockquote><br />\n我個d 暗粒好麻煩 食好耐先推到出黎<br />\n同埋好多疤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上美國網睇過, 其實每日劑量都有講究<br />\n要夠體重 (kg) x 0.5mg 一日先有效<br />\n跟佢計法我要食40mg 先過到數"},{"pid":"e4e162ca327b0e7fef0e64ffc42fb21a8af4c1f6","tid":102131,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:14:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登有冇食A 酸既朋友? 有野想指教一下<br />\n我食左四個月20mg 醫生叫我自己決定停唔停藥<br />\n但其實有一邊面 康復進度唔理想<br />\n但佢成日話算好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同劑量有冇關係? 佢有講再食就要40mg 一日</blockquote><br />\n我都食左快半年，私家醫生，佢話正常黎講一個療程係6-9個月，我係完全一粒都唔生得番d印佢先話可以停，如果壓抑得唔夠耐同穩定會容易復發。</blockquote><br />\nbtw 我都係私家<br />\n好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59038e26c627e9fb91601f9926bcc98f0288d91b","tid":102131,"uid":15070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:22:45.000Z","msg":"食30 三個月 啲暗粒仲出緊 想死"},{"pid":"f40ad34e26f7f6e01d003fa4ca20bf19b4a832c7","tid":102131,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:27:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食30 三個月 啲暗粒仲出緊 想死</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  本身情況如何"},{"pid":"cfcc83024aaabcfeb16500eaa186253970b800c0","tid":102131,"uid":15070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食30 三個月 啲暗粒仲出緊 想死</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  本身情況如何</blockquote><br />\n而家同未食前差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1201772a5c491cacb35fd7e415f2f934c5db487d","tid":102131,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:55:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食30 三個月 啲暗粒仲出緊 想死</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  本身情況如何</blockquote><br />\n而家同未食前差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  3 個月都冇用?"},{"pid":"305d97f609868782bf4ddd2e8f77e3f5dc8881f0","tid":102131,"uid":15070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  本身情況如何</blockquote><br />\n而家同未食前差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  3 個月都冇用?</blockquote><br />\n開頭爆發期好差 而家好返啲 咪變返未食之前咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af5d2f04333fa1e66e7db29f4f54349bf100ca7","tid":102131,"uid":52608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:38:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>連登有冇食A 酸既朋友? 有野想指教一下<br />\n我食左四個月20mg 醫生叫我自己決定停唔停藥<br />\n但其實有一邊面 康復進度唔理想<br />\n但佢成日話算好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同劑量有冇關係? 佢有講再食就要40mg 一日</blockquote><br />\n我都食左快半年，私家醫生，佢話正常黎講一個療程係6-9個月，我係完全一粒都唔生得番d印佢先話可以停，如果壓抑得唔夠耐同穩定會容易復發。</blockquote><br />\n我個d 暗粒好麻煩 食好耐先推到出黎<br />\n同埋好多疤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上美國網睇過, 其實每日劑量都有講究<br />\n要夠體重 (kg) x 0.5mg 一日先有效<br />\n跟佢計法我要食40mg 先過到數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一開始食20mg先，食左一兩個月身體適應先加到30mg，醫生話我體重30mg夠，除非30mg都壓抑唔到先再加，同埋keep住要驗肝，個醫生都nice同埋謹慎嘅，但真係好貴，一個月差唔多$3000，不過真係work，依家一粒都無。遲d考慮做埋激光去印。"},{"pid":"5704225e421066260063c70e45763fc7b35f94bd","tid":102131,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:58:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我都食左快半年，私家醫生，佢話正常黎講一個療程係6-9個月，我係完全一粒都唔生得番d印佢先話可以停，如果壓抑得唔夠耐同穩定會容易復發。</blockquote><br />\n我個d 暗粒好麻煩 食好耐先推到出黎<br />\n同埋好多疤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上美國網睇過, 其實每日劑量都有講究<br />\n要夠體重 (kg) x 0.5mg 一日先有效<br />\n跟佢計法我要食40mg 先過到數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一開始食20mg先，食左一兩個月身體適應先加到30mg，醫生話我體重30mg夠，除非30mg都壓抑唔到先再加，同埋keep住要驗肝，個醫生都nice同埋謹慎嘅，但真係好貴，一個月差唔多$3000，不過真係work，依家一粒都無。遲d考慮做埋激光去印。</blockquote><br />\n我個case 係好多萬年recurrent acne / 粉刺<br />\n每一個月就清到少少<br />\n但一邊面冇乜用<br />\n<br />\n咁你覺得20mg 30mg 分別大唔大?"},{"pid":"742c1aa89de6fbab8645536d8c4f0c83c930a98d","tid":102131,"uid":25055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:17:00.000Z","msg":"食緊20mg第四個月<br />\n正面一粒都無爆瘡<br />\n但獲獲都爆太陽穴兩邊果個位<br />\n爆完一粒 一陣再生d大頭瘡"},{"pid":"625008dc59cccc71532a01c4a0e27818aa22fe27","tid":102131,"uid":52608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:48:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我個d 暗粒好麻煩 食好耐先推到出黎<br />\n同埋好多疤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上美國網睇過, 其實每日劑量都有講究<br />\n要夠體重 (kg) x 0.5mg 一日先有效<br />\n跟佢計法我要食40mg 先過到數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一開始食20mg先，食左一兩個月身體適應先加到30mg，醫生話我體重30mg夠，除非30mg都壓抑唔到先再加，同埋keep住要驗肝，個醫生都nice同埋謹慎嘅，但真係好貴，一個月差唔多$3000，不過真係work，依家一粒都無。遲d考慮做埋激光去印。</blockquote><br />\n我個case 係好多萬年recurrent acne / 粉刺<br />\n每一個月就清到少少<br />\n但一邊面冇乜用<br />\n<br />\n咁你覺得20mg 30mg 分別大唔大?</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n都大嘅，食30mg開始就進入穩定期，生少左，基本第4個月開始已經淨係偶然一兩粒新生嘅。第5、6個月已經無再生。唯一就係，劑量越大，皮膚越容易乾，乾到起曬皮。醫生話我進度都幾好，有d人食好耐都未咁快有效果。"},{"pid":"a862b2879797df822e8bac85080d73fdd72d3756","tid":102131,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:54:48.000Z","msg":"6個月完左，日日m記夜訓冇問題，印都慢慢淡了（半年前完療程）"},{"pid":"a0782495d19b5f4f0fd516dc96220309b2fef7dc","tid":102131,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:56:58.000Z","msg":"醫生正常會幫你計體重，然後計到要食幾多mg之後先斷到尾，唔好半途而廢就算而家停咗生暗瘡都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a82e27561cb57d664007c7aada568a48ca76757","tid":102131,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫生正常會幫你計體重，然後計到要食幾多mg之後先斷到尾，唔好半途而廢就算而家停咗生暗瘡都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係20mg x 4months 咋<br />\n想跟體重先正式計數<br />\n40mg 一日都要食多4 個月<br />\n成萬銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc037d3b76ea966ba18c6d79336c883d15e58938","tid":102131,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:45:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>醫生正常會幫你計體重，然後計到要食幾多mg之後先斷到尾，唔好半途而廢就算而家停咗生暗瘡都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係20mg x 4months 咋<br />\n想跟體重先正式計數<br />\n40mg 一日都要食多4 個月<br />\n成萬銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我56kg食左6個月既20mg...<br />\n雖然唔知你幾重，但點都食夠6個月好！<br />\n早啲訓啦 傷肝呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d3da6b8f9bb03479d747f508056b7111fc7d1b","tid":102131,"uid":55456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:47:07.000Z","msg":"其實食A酸話會皮膚乾係食個陣先有 定一世都係咁??<br />\n<br />\n食A酸會唔會幫手去埋印??"},{"pid":"7e5259cd46bd642fa67eede8b589c61eeea0d51b","tid":102131,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實食A酸話會皮膚乾係食個陣先有 定一世都係咁??<br />\n<br />\n食A酸會唔會幫手去埋印??</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食個排先乾<br />\n唔多唔少醫生講過話有美容效果...<br />\n其實唔再生之後，皮膚會變好左，印會慢慢淡。"},{"pid":"da4598601900f3902c51dfb7b600f266d54e7a5e","tid":102131,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:11:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>醫生正常會幫你計體重，然後計到要食幾多mg之後先斷到尾，唔好半途而廢就算而家停咗生暗瘡都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係20mg x 4months 咋<br />\n想跟體重先正式計數<br />\n40mg 一日都要食多4 個月<br />\n成萬銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我56kg食左6個月既20mg...<br />\n雖然唔知你幾重，但點都食夠6個月好！<br />\n早啲訓啦 傷肝呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差唔多70kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b537d7b72332931d233c2df45400893b70a35e2","tid":102131,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:13:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實食A酸話會皮膚乾係食個陣先有 定一世都係咁??<br />\n<br />\n食A酸會唔會幫手去埋印??</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食個排先乾<br />\n唔多唔少醫生講過話有美容效果...<br />\n其實唔再生之後，皮膚會變好左，印會慢慢淡。</blockquote><br />\nno<br />\n食個排會大約冇左8成面油分泌<br />\n<br />\n療程會令皮脂腺會永久縮小<br />\n停藥後會多番少少油, around 療程前一半左右"},{"pid":"cd8324ad98127dc82bc2b98fd2a76527985c57cc","tid":102131,"uid":72826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:22:40.000Z","msg":"最近比暗粒困擾左好多個月都唔好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲好反覆 好少少但一夜訓就瘋狂爆 想問 其實你地嚴重去到咩情況下先去食a酸?"},{"pid":"ace204188308e677cf60db98f5172490d258f064","tid":102131,"uid":55456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:23:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實食A酸話會皮膚乾係食個陣先有 定一世都係咁??<br />\n<br />\n食A酸會唔會幫手去埋印??</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食個排先乾<br />\n唔多唔少醫生講過話有美容效果...<br />\n其實唔再生之後，皮膚會變好左，印會慢慢淡。</blockquote><br />\nno<br />\n食個排會大約冇左8成面油分泌<br />\n<br />\n療程會令皮脂腺會永久縮小<br />\n停藥後會多番少少油, around 療程前一半左右</blockquote><br />\n咁我而家少出暗瘡但好多暗粒應該點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋而家有好多印 最近有啲係條頸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲係到差唔多2年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e56d0224a59b4272e911b7fa61d70b1e99d34e","tid":102131,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:27:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近比暗粒困擾左好多個月都唔好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲好反覆 好少少但一夜訓就瘋狂爆 想問 其實你地嚴重去到咩情況下先去食a酸?</blockquote><br />\n好似武功咁有分十級程度<br />\n自己judge 唔到就去問下醫生吧<br />\n我果個話3 級已經要做treatment<br />\n當然唔一定要A 酸"},{"pid":"fdceeac51e34b59c8f7927f726b4ab35a32a4b18","tid":102131,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:31:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食個排先乾<br />\n唔多唔少醫生講過話有美容效果...<br />\n其實唔再生之後，皮膚會變好左，印會慢慢淡。</blockquote><br />\nno<br />\n食個排會大約冇左8成面油分泌<br />\n<br />\n療程會令皮脂腺會永久縮小<br />\n停藥後會多番少少油, around 療程前一半左右</blockquote><br />\n咁我而家少出暗瘡但好多暗粒應該點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋而家有好多印 最近有啲係條頸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲係到差唔多2年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係醫生唔亂答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只可以講隻藥暗粒都有幫助<br />\n印就兩睇啦<br />\n你諗下自己長時間唔再爆豆, 加上d 皮膚結構穩定緊, 自己會慢慢淡<br />\n相反,疤痕就接近0 效用<br />\nsource 我自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}